                   =  |        +-----------+ |  =
                   =  +----------------------+  =
                   ==============================


     The intervals  can  be  played  through  a  synthesiser  if  it's
connected to the computer via a Midi interface. When activate the midi
output, the sound will be redirected  to  the synthesiser and you will
hear nothing through the computer.  You  can choose the instrument and
the channel number that must be used for playing the interval.
@endnode

