@node StartQuiz
                           ================
                           =              =
                           =  Start quiz  =
                           =              =
                           ================


     This does the same  as  the  'Start  quiz'  gadget  in the report
window. Use it to start a quiz.
@endnode

@node StopQuiz
                           ===============
                           =             =
