@node Tips
                              ==========
                              =        =
                              =  Tips  =
                              =        =
                              ==========


     I'll give you some tips about  how to learn the intervals easily.
Before starting you should  search  for  tunes  or melodies that begin
with a certain interval.
     E.g. : Love-story begins with a minor sixth (C E E C C)
            My Way begins with a major sixth (E C# E C# B C#)

     Before starting a quiz you should  press the button gadget of the
intervals that you plan to do a  quiz with. When you hear the computer
playing the interval, try to sing  the  appropriate melody with it. Do
this for every interval that you  when  to  be tested with. Only start
the quiz when you're able  to  sing  every selected interval for every
selected root.

     When the computer plays an interval during the quiz, try to match
the correct melody  with  it.  Once  you're  able  to  do  so, you can
distinguish the interval.

     After some time you'll begin  to  'feel'  which interval is being
played. You can then  forget  about  the  melody  and just follow your
feelings. It's this stage that you should try to reach because this is
the only way it's going to be useful to you.
@endnode

